        "setup": "Go to the [API keys dashboard](https://gojinko.com/dashboard/keys), sign in, and click **Create key**. The key is shown once and starts with `jnk_`. Copy it into your secret store immediately. Use the same key for REST, the CLI (`jinko auth login --key ...` or `JINKO_API_KEY`), and MCP clients that need direct bearer auth. Jinko uses separate keys for production and sandbox.",
